{
  "stem": "8784.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But for the next few days, we did not do much else than go out to the back yard for counting and recounting of us and-- and occasional beatings of-- of us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The SS guards there had a nasty habit of kick-- kicking people, kicking people until a person would fall to the ground.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when that person looked unconscious or unhappy enough, the SS guards would leave him alone again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But this was their-- their habit in that concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We stayed in this one-- in this one barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if I recall it, the center of that barrack had a very nice, clean room that looked like a kitchen with pots and pans hanging in there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it looked like a-- a respectable kind of a place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I-- I know now what this was for, and this was for the ready inspections.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In case the Red Cross or somebody would come in to a camp, they would take them through this-- through this center room, and they would see how orderly the prisoners are kept in those rooms, and evidently food supply was there.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But our food was-- once a day, we received some kind of a thin soup of something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whatever was in it, we don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I know that we were waken up at the-- at a godly hour of 4 o'clock when it was extremely dark yet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is October night, very dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We would be waken up to go to the mess hall and receive this soup, and-- and they divvy it up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I remember them dishing out that soup in that camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
